## Carpathians host 8 karst springs from 3 countries.

Slovakian data is provided by Peter Malik (peter.malik@geology.sk) 
Czechian data is recommended by Pavel Pracny (pracny@sci.muni.cz)
Serbian data is obtained from WOKAS database.

The original source of the Slovakian data is Slovakian Hydrometeorological Service "https://www.shmu.sk/sk/?page=2649" 
The data source of the Czechian karst springs is National Hydrological Database of Czechia "https://isvs.chmi.cz/ords/f?p=11002:2:105656156435140:::RP,2:P2_SEQ:%5C759%5C" 

For more information, please see Metadata table.
